<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mindmap | The Midnight Visitor</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2c3e50;
            --accent: #e74c3c;
            --bg: #f4f7f6;
            --text: #333;
            --white: #ffffff;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--white);
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 2.5rem; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        p.subtitle { opacity: 0.8; font-style: italic; }

        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            border-top: 5px solid var(--accent);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        h2 {
            color: var(--primary);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }

        li::before {
            content: '•';
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            top: -5px;
        }

        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>THE MIDNIGHT VISITOR</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">A Visual Mindmap of Robert Arthur's Classic Story</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        
        <div class="card">
            <h2>👥 Key Characters</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="highlight">Ausable:</span> A secret agent who looks "fat and sloppy" but possesses extreme wit.</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">Max:</span> The antagonist; a slender, crafty spy who threatens Ausable with a pistol.</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">Fowler:</span> A young writer who expects a romantic, thrill-filled spy story.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>🏨 The Setting</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="highlight">Location:</span> A musty French hotel room.</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">The Floor:</span> 6th and top floor௮crucial for the "balcony" lie.</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">Atmosphere:</span> Dull and uninspiring until the intruder appears.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>🎭 The Master Plan</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="highlight">The Lie:</span> Ausable complains about a non-existent balcony to plant the idea in Max's mind.</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">The "Police":</span> When a knock is heard, Ausable claims it's the police arriving for protection.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>🏁 The Resolution</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="highlight">The Jump:</span> Max, panicked by the "police," jumps into the dark to hide on the "balcony."</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">The Reality:</span> There was no balcony. Max falls to the ground.</li>
                <li><span class="highlight">The Visitor:</span> The person at the door was actually Henry, the waiter.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        Interactive Mindmap Concept &bull; Created for Educational Purposes
    </div>

</body>
</html>
